core

### Is this a regression?

No

### Description

I wanted to trigger a reload function based on changes of my input signal. But if i only used it in the if-statement check it doesn't trigger the effect. Only when I assign it to a e.g. `const` it works fine.

Doesn't work:
```TypeScript
constructor() {
  effect(() => {
    if (this.inputSignal()) {
      this.reloadData();
    }
  });
}
```

Works fine:
```TypeScript
constructor() {
  effect(() => {
    const a = this.inputSignal();
    if (a) {
      this.reloadData();
    }
  });
}
```

